resources.string:
MSU Parking Tips is a helpful guide 
 to find FREE parking on campus!
 You can begin my clicking the 
 "Search for parking button", on 
 the previous page. This will then 
 generate a list of the nearest 
 parking lots. You can then click 
 on any of the parking lots to 
 get details on times, locations, 
 and pricing (specifically when 
 there is free parking).
